                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这个点钻的挺透。没白瞎时间。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="948537592">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-948537592" class="vote-count">5</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-948537592" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="948537592">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/38928437/">臭包子</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-08-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">超级好书！岂止是旅蒙商，简直蒙古国兴亡的大题材！行文流畅，思路清晰，又有很多机巧聪明之处，把渺小个人在残酷历史中挣扎的无助感表现的淋漓尽致！唏嘘……强烈推荐大家都读一读……</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

